{{setvar::VisualStyle::## 📄 Plain Text

No HTML. No CSS. No special character effects. Clean prose only.

Write in plain text throughout. No color spans, no styled elements, no unicode glyph effects, no glowing text. When runes appear in the story, describe them in prose. When a computer screen displays something, narrate what it says. When a neon sign flickers, write the sentence.

The formatting is the prose. Nothing else.}}

